This python script is modified from OrgaQuant https://github.com/TKassis/OrgaQuant . It is used for bright field picture based organoids detection and quantification. 

To set up:
1. Follow the instruction to install OrgaQuant in a python virtual environment: https://github.com/TKassis/OrgaQuant
2. Create a directory under the Orgaquant called plugin/ . Move statistics.py and visualization.py into it
3. Edit the input, output directories and other parameters in orgaquant_run.py

To run the script:
1. Activate orgaquant virtual environment in terminal
2. Run python orgaquant_run.py instead of orgaquant.py
